    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/4890658e677f86faf3b0224eb1306402_7737560170156973498.png",
                "key": "洑流剑",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "洑流剑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，若角色未附属<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">佩伊刻计</span>，则使其附属<span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">佩伊刻计</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">佩伊刻计</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方每抓1张牌后：</span>此牌累积1层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「压力阶级」</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色使用浮冰增压时：</span>如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「压力阶级」</span>至少有2层，则移除此效果，使技能少花费1元素骰，且如果此技能结算后<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「压力阶级」</span>至少有4层，则再额外造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/c1d00d4cc7aceb1da905d0a18a377067_7835017071254937285.png",
                "key": "浮冰增压",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "浮冰增压"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">潜猎模式</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">潜猎模式</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方抓3张牌后：</span>提供1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">护盾</span>，保护所附属角色。（可叠加，最多叠加至2点）。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附属角色使用普通攻击或元素战技后：</span>将原本元素骰费用最高的至多2张手牌置于牌库底，然后抓等量的牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/ffdac7f3b8ba78be1c835200568616da_4319060414960947384.png",
                "key": "猎影潜袭",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "猎影潜袭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/f0235ce442adeb6ea4e53e325614d3a5_1203916215823779940.png",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_6742357886851042591.png",
                "key": "规则术语",
